value.name: Treason
value.overview: An MI6 deputy's bright future takes a sharp turn after a reunion with a Russian spy forces him to question his entire life.

value.name: Gunpowder, Treason & Plot
value.overview: Mini series depicting the turbulent and bloody reigns of Scottish monarchs Mary, Queen of Scots and her son King James VI of Scotland who became King James I of England and foiled the Gunpowder Plot.

value.name: The Genius Prince's Guide to Raising a Nation Out of Debt
value.original_name: 天才王子の赤字国家再生術
value.overview: Prince Wein is ready to commit treason. And who can blame him? Faced with the impossible task of ruling his pathetic little kingdom, this poor guy just can't catch a break! But with his brilliant idea of auctioning off his country, this lazy prince should be able to retire once and for all. Or that was the plan...until his treasonous schemes lead to disastrous consequences-namely, accidental victories and the favor of his people!
